'''豬門事件'''（{{lang-en|Piggate}}）是一件與前[[英國首相|英國首相]][[大衛·卡麥隆|大衛·卡麥隆]]相關的未經證實的軼事，相傳在他大學期間，曾將他的[[陰莖|陰莖]]和/或[[睪丸|睪丸]]插入死豬的嘴裡，作為[[牛津大學|牛津大學]][[皮爾斯格威斯頓社|皮爾斯格威斯頓社]]入社儀式的一部分。{{tsl|en|Michael Ashcroft|邁克爾·阿什克羅夫特}}和{{tsl|en|Isabel Oakeshott|伊莎貝爾·奧克肖特}}在未經授權的卡麥隆傳記《Call Me Dave》中報導了這則軼事，並稱這個故事來源於一位匿名的國會議員。本書摘錄於2015年9月20日出版前在《[[每日郵報|每日郵報]]》上發表。

[[唐寧街|唐寧街]]的消息人士回應說，當時的[[英國首相|首相]][[大衛·卡麥隆|卡麥隆]]不會以正面回應來糾正這件事，卡麥隆後來表示，“已經於一周前作出了非常具體的否認”。

阿什克羅夫特（Ashcroft）和奧克肖特（Oakeshott）未能從自稱該事件照片的所有人那裡得到答覆，而且該事件刊出以來，尚無確鑿的證據來支持這一軼事。

[[皮爾斯格威斯頓社|皮爾斯格威斯頓社]]創始人之一瓦倫丁·吉尼斯（Valentine Guinness）在一次採訪中說，卡麥隆“很可能參加了他們的一場聚會”，但據他所知，他從來都不是該社的會員。

==奇聞軼事==
據稱，作為[[牛津大學|牛津大學]]的一名學生，前[[英國首相|英國首相]][[大衛·卡麥隆|大衛·卡麥隆]]（David Cameron）將“解剖學上的私密部位”插入了一隻死豬的嘴中，作為[[皮爾斯格威斯頓社|皮爾斯格威斯頓社]]（Piers Gaveston Society）入會儀式的一部分。

==背景==
阿什克羅夫特勳爵長期以來一直是[[英國保守黨|英國保守黨]]的支持者，並且是英國保守黨的最大捐助者，捐贈了約1000萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]。在2013年，由於與大衛·卡麥隆的衝突，他放棄了對該黨的支持，尤其是儘管他對黨貢獻良多卡麥隆仍拒絕賦予他一個高級職位。<ref>{{cite news|title=Lord Ashcroft's Cameron biography bears hallmarks of revenge job|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/sep/21/lord-ashcrofts-cameron-biography-bears-hallmarks-of-revenge-job|access-date=2015-09-22|work=The Guardian|location=London|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111172001/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/sep/21/lord-ashcrofts-cameron-biography-bears-hallmarks-of-revenge-job|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://time.com/4043311/david-cameron-pig-gate-scandal/|title=Why David Cameron’s 'Pig-Gate' Scandal Isn't Going Away|work=TIME|access-date=2015-09-21|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124021130/https://time.com/4043311/david-cameron-pig-gate-scandal/|dead-url=no}}</ref>一些評論家將書中的“豬的故事”和其他軼事解釋為阿什克羅夫特對卡麥隆的仇恨和報仇。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.spectator.co.uk/steerpike/2015/09/lord-ashcroft-gets-his-revenge-on-david-cameron-piggate/|title=Lord Ashcroft gets his revenge on David Cameron: #piggate|work=The Spectator|access-date=2015-09-21|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923060118/http://blogs.spectator.co.uk/steerpike/2015/09/lord-ashcroft-gets-his-revenge-on-david-cameron-piggate/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/11878948/Lord-Ashcroft-reignites-bitter-feud-with-David-Cameron.html|title=Lord Ashcroft reignites bitter feud with David Cameron|work=The Daily Telegraph|location=London|access-date=2015-09-21|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030173029/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/11878948/Lord-Ashcroft-reignites-bitter-feud-with-David-Cameron.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==回覆==
在被問到這件趣聞之後，[[唐寧街|唐寧街]]表示，它們不會通過正面回應來“端正”這一件事。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/george-osborne-refuses-to-comment-on-claims-that-david-cameron-put-his-genitals-in-a-dead-pigs-mouth-at-university-10510692.html|title=David Cameron says he 'will not dignify' claims he put his genitals in the mouth of a dead pig|work=The Independent|location=London|access-date=2015-09-25|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923063550/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/george-osborne-refuses-to-comment-on-claims-that-david-cameron-put-his-genitals-in-a-dead-pigs-mouth-at-university-10510692.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/downing-street-stays-silent-over-claims-david-cameron-put-genitals-in-a-dead-pigs-mouth-while-at-oxford-university-10510500.html|title=Downing Street stays silent over claims David Cameron put genitals in a dead pig's mouth while at Oxford University|work=The Independent|location=London|access-date=2015-09-21|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923073825/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/downing-street-stays-silent-over-claims-david-cameron-put-genitals-in-a-dead-pigs-mouth-while-at-oxford-university-10510500.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》報導說，卡麥隆曾告訴朋友，這一說法“完全是胡說八道”。<ref name="The Independent">{{cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/dead-pig-allegations-are-utter-nonsense-david-cameron-tells-friends-10511399.html|title=Dead pig allegations are 'utter nonsense,' David Cameron tells friends|work=The Independent|location=London|date=2015-09-21|access-date=2015-09-25|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113191533/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/dead-pig-allegations-are-utter-nonsense-david-cameron-tells-friends-10511399.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>卡麥隆直到9月23日才在自己的[[Twitter|Twitter]]帳戶上發布推文，隨後他收到了一系列與豬性交有關的回覆。<ref name="nsubuga">{{cite news|url=http://metro.co.uk/2015/09/24/david-cameron-tweeted-for-the-first-time-since-piggate-and-it-didnt-go-very-well-5405621/|title=David Cameron tweeted for the first time since #piggate and it didn’t go very well|work=Metro|author=Jimmy Nsubuga|date=2015-09-24|accessdate=2021-02-18|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123174748/https://metro.co.uk/2015/09/24/david-cameron-tweeted-for-the-first-time-since-piggate-and-it-didnt-go-very-well-5405621/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="allegretti">{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2015/09/23/david-cameron-piggate_n_8184162.html|title=David Cameron Given Searing Reaction By Twitter Users After First Post Since #Piggate|work=The Huffington Post UK|author=Aubrey Allegretti|date=2015-09-23|accessdate=2021-02-18|archive-date=2018-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915074639/https://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2015/09/23/david-cameron-piggate_n_8184162.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

卡麥隆在當週晚些時候在牛津的一次談話中對該事件開了個玩笑。事件發生六天後，卡麥隆回答了一個有關該事件的問題。

==社會反應==
在《每日郵報》發布有關這則軼事的文章的幾分鐘內，＃piggate、＃snoutrage和#hameron<ref name="guardian1">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/sep/21/piggate-hameron-twitter-react-david-cameron-pig-head-claims|title=From #piggate to #Hameron: how Twitter reacted to David Cameron claims|work=The Guardian|location=London|access-date=2015-09-23|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308192538/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2015/sep/21/piggate-hameron-twitter-react-david-cameron-pig-head-claims|dead-url=no}}</ref>成為[[Twitter|Twitter]]上的流行話題。<ref name="guardian1"/>“ Piggate”該詞很快被媒體報導接受<ref>{{cite web|url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2015/09/21/what-piggate-really-says-about-the-state-of-british-politics/|title=What #PigGate Really Says About the State of British Politics|work=Foreign Policy|access-date=2015-09-23|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514082734/https://foreignpolicy.com/2015/09/21/what-piggate-really-says-about-the-state-of-british-politics/|dead-url=no}}</ref>(醜聞經常以“-gate”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://public.oed.com/aspects-of-english/english-in-use/the-gate-suffix/ |title=The ‘gate’ suffix |work=[[Oxford_English_Dictionary|Oxford English Dictionary]] |access-date=2021-02-18 |archive-date=2018-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180221231841/http://public.oed.com/aspects-of-english/english-in-use/the-gate-suffix/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>為後綴)。

該軼事出現後，[[社群媒體|社群媒體]]用戶迅速將該事件與著名[[影集|影集]]《[[黑鏡|黑鏡]]》中的第一季第一集《[[國歌_(黑鏡)|國歌]]》做連結，該故事描述虛構的英國首相在遭脅迫下與豬發生性關係。劇集作者[[查理·布魯克|查理·布魯克]]（Charlie Brooker）很快否認了有關指控的任何先驗知識，稱這種情況“是完全的巧合，儘管這是一個很奇怪的現象。”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vox.com/2015/9/21/9365507/piggate-david-cameron-piers-galverston|title=9 questions about David Cameron's #PigGate you were too embarrassed to ask|work=Vox|access-date=2015-09-21|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410192351/https://www.vox.com/2015/9/21/9365507/piggate-david-cameron-piers-galverston|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/shortcuts/2015/sep/21/pigs-prime-minister-black-mirror-ashcroft-allegation-charlie-brooker|title=Charlie Brooker on Cameron and #piggate: 'I'd have been screaming it into traffic if I'd known'|work=The Guardian|location=London|access-date=2015-09-21|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923010128/http://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/shortcuts/2015/sep/21/pigs-prime-minister-black-mirror-ashcroft-allegation-charlie-brooker|dead-url=no}}</ref>

